{"tid":649378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【審查教科書】政總網站突刪「主權移交」字眼","createTime":"2018-05-01T13:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T15:43:36.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9989dddde6781ea381f36fa3c6911f9686607cc4","tid":649378,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"一定又係IT狗的錯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180501/58141652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58141652&d=ezadUHsncOyg%2Flh2GMxjIosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=59e8379e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58141652&h=bcc1d89e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180501/58141652</a><br />\n<br />\n 繼歷史教科書「香港主權移交中國內地」字眼被教育局評審報告指「措辭不恰當」，政府總部禮賓處網站亦將「主權移交」字眼刪除。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》報道，禮賓處在該報查詢使用有關字眼的指引後，移除英文版網站原有的「主權移交」（handover of sovereignty）字眼。涉事句子原為「自1997年7月1日主權移交以來，一些外國的國家或政府領袖曾訪問香港」（Since the handover of sovereignty over Hong Kong on 1 July 1997, a number of foreign state or government leaders have visited Hong Kong.），改動後該句只以「自1997年7月1日」（Since July 1, 1997）開首。<br />\n<br />\n至於網站的中文版，報道指同一段落的「主權移交」字眼同樣被刪除，但在另一段落中仍有「主權移交」字眼。現時網站中文版首段字眼開首為「每年，訪港的外國顯要眾多。香港自主權移交以來，貴賓的訪問活動愈趨頻繁。」第二段開首則為「1997年7月1日以來，已有超過100位國家元首、政府首腦和高級部長級別的外國主要官員，於『正式訪問計劃』下獲邀訪港。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》已向政府總部禮賓處查詢，正等待回覆。"},{"pid":"161671da1eab3d3ce193a8209d6a7f17258d532c","tid":649378,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"463afbe022c6481fa5a6acfbabf185b638b8e93d","tid":649378,"uid":126731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T14:14:04.000Z","msg":"即係支持還返香港俾大英袓國?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08ee4e507b3f2f737ffbfd455ed04b53bc55ce2